    <h1 class="fs-1 fw-bold text-center mt-5 shadow-lg p-3 mb-5 bg-info rounded ">Return & Refund Policy </h1>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >RETURN POLICY:</h5>
		<p>Our goal is to make sure all of our customers are 100% satisfied. If you're not happy with your purchase, you may return it within 30 days of the order date for a full refund. It is worth noting that our refunds and returns do not support cross-border.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >Return shipping fee: </h5>
		<p>Thee is no restocking fee. 

There is no cost  for returning  in case  case of this happens when the product is incorrect, damaged by the carrier or defective in another way

 You will be responsible for paying actual shipping cost for your own shipping costs for returning your item in case of  purchased the wrong product, it doesn't fit or they no longer want the item  .

conditions: product condition should be new and with same label ,packaging in box to meet our return policy</p>
	</div>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >HOW TO RETURN:</h5>
		<p>Please contact us to initiate your return at perafin.parvej@gmail.com
		Please provide us with your order number, item(s) being returned, and the reason for return.
Return labels can be provided with the cost of return shipping deducted from your refund. You may also choose to mail the item back using your own insured, traceable method. We are not responsible for items that are lost or damaged in the mail.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >DAMAGED AND DEFECTIVE PRODUCTS:</h5>
		<p>We suggest that you inspect all packaging received for any defects. If your item is damaged or defective please contact us immediately and we will work with you. Damaged or defective items will be replaced.
We will require images of the damages to the product and of the original packaging received along with its shipping label.
Damaged items need to be reported within 3 days of receipt. Once your return request has been received, our customer care team will reach out to you within 1 business day.

Your product must be unused and in the same condition as you received it, be sure to keep the original packaging. If you have taken apart or used the product, we cannot accept your request.
Any item that is not in its original condition, or that is damaged or has missing parts due to a cause other than a manufacturer's defect, may not be eligible for return.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >REFUNDS (IF APPLICABLE):</h5>
		<p>Once your return is received, we will send you an email to notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify you of the approval or rejection of your refund.
If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment.

Please fill out the contact form to contact customer service to replace defective or mis-delivered items. We will request an image of the damaged product as well as an image of the original packaging received and its shipping label.
 We may send you a shipping label to return the original item.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >LATE OR MISSING REFUNDS (IF APPLICABLE):</h5>
		<p>If you haven't received your refund, please check your bank account again first.
Contact your credit card company and it may take a while for your refund to be officially issued.
If you've done all of this and still haven't received your refund, please contact us at perafin.parvej@gmail.com..</p>
	</div>
	<div class="px-5">
	<h5 >CANCEL THE ORDER:</h5>
		<p>We start processing your order as soon as you submit it, so we cannot cancel, edit or add products to your order after you have completed it.
	<br>
Email: perafin.parvej@gmail.com <br>
Phone: 01521431055 <br>

Operating Hours: 9am - 5pm EST Monday to Friday</p>
